combinedPhrases.text: Hi there, thank you for calling Contoso. My name is Sam. How can I help you today? Good afternoon, my name is Mary Adams. I want to buy life insurance for my husband. Can you please tell me how much it costs? I'm going to help you right now with your life insurance needs. Are you the owner of the policy? My husband and I are the owners of the policy, so I will be paying for the policy myself, but I want him to be protected in case something happens to me. Good. What type of policy are you looking for? We have term life, whole life, universal life, etc. Term would be perfect for us, but can you please tell me how much the monthly payment would be for term life with $500,000 of coverage? If you pay $30 each month, your husband will be insured for a total of $500,000 of coverage with a monthly premium of $30. How often would we have to pay this premium? You will pay this premium every month until you reach age 100 or your husband dies, whichever happens first. Would you like to schedule a payment date so that your husband can start receiving his insurance coverage? Yes. How soon can you schedule it? Let me see if there are any open dates for today or tomorrow. Would that work for you? That is fine with me. OK, Mrs. Adams, I have an opening tomorrow morning at 10:00 AM and 1:00 PM. Would either of those times work for you? Yes, I can do 10 a.m. tomorrow morning. Great. I will call you tomorrow morning at 9:45 a.m. with payment instructions and confirmation information. Is that okay? That sounds great. I'll talk to you tomorrow morning at 9:45 a.m.
